      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age in several areas. The exterior has some noticeable scratches and a small dent on the rear passenger door, while the interior upholstery shows significant wear and some staining. Mechanically, the car starts and runs consistently, but it will likely require some suspension work and a new set of tires in the near future. It\u2019s a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle who doesn't mind a bit of character and a few upcoming maintenance tasks.",
