      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 1997 Porsche 911 Carrera represents the pinnacle of air-cooled engineering. It features the 3.6L M64 flat-six engine equipped with the VarioRam induction system, delivering linear power across the entire rev range. Mated to a precise G50 6-speed manual transaxle, the drivetrain remains tight and leak-free. The chassis utilizes the sophisticated multi-link rear suspension with kinematic toe adjustment, ensuring telepathic handling. This example is in museum-grade condition, with original cosmoline still visible on the undercarriage and zero oxidation on the heat exchangers. The factory ventilated rotors and four-piston Brembo calipers show no signs of thermal stress. A truly turn-key collector piece.",
